text: Escambia County is a county in the U.S. state of Florida. It was formed on July 21, 1821. As of 2020, 321,905 people lived there. Escambia County's seat is Pensacola. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official county website Category:Florida counties Category:1821 establishments in the United States Category:1820s establishments in Florida Territory
